<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> cōḍakulatilaka <gap reason="lost" quantity="15" unit="character"/> rājēṁdra vīrama
<lb n="3" break="no"/>hēṁdra vikramacōḍa vijayābharaṇa rājakēsarivarmma permmānaḍigalu gaṁggākāvērīparyyaṁta<unclear>dhari</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>trīpati saptamōviṣṇuvarddhanulaina tribhuvanacakravartti śrīkulōttuṁggacōḍadēvara pravarddha<unclear>mā</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>navijayarājyasaṁvatsara 33 ṇḍagu śrāhi dina 330 ṇṭaṁ pērūri [Āṁ]ḍiseṭṭi tama taṇḍri Acci
<lb n="6" break="no"/>seṭṭikiṁgā śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍava<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>tti lōhadaṇḍudiviya 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīni
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ki Ācaṁdrārkkamu neyi sariyiṁccuvārugā dēvara kilaramuna prōlebōla nāviya
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yi kommabhōla nāviyayi cadukanā jakkiyayi bādabōla Eṟiyanayi be
<lb n="9" break="no"/>rasina bōlu nalvuru pūṁṭagānu prōlabōla nāviya Aḍapuna nāvabōla musi
<lb n="10" break="no"/>yani vasamunaṁ beṭṭina InupaEḍlu 50 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nityapaḍi vōyaṁggala tribhuvanāṁ
<lb n="11" break="no"/><unclear>ku</unclear>śamuna nē mā 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> likhitaḥ vīrarājēṁdracōḍaĀcāryyaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
